These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving, traveling
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the fan of pop and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Hobby      | skydiving | traveling | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, chess, snooker
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the person playing scrabble##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Game   | scrabble    | snooker        | chess |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, canasta
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing chess is between the owner of the ferret and the person playing canasta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Game   | backgammon | chess     | canasta |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, soul
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, bridge
1. the fan of funk is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the fan of soul is between the person playing snooker and the person playing mah-jongg##2
3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | soul     | funk |
| Game           | snooker | bridge | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, vegafina, ritmeester
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Cigar   | vegafina | ritmeester     | bolivar |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, go, backgammon
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing scrabble##2
2. the person playing scrabble is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Game   | scrabble  | go   | backgammon        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
House: craftsman, victorian, futuristic
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the craftsman house is between the person eating pineapple and the victorian house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| House   | victorian | craftsman | futuristic     |

