.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake, pony
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the owner of the snake is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the pony##2
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Pet   | pony   | rabbit  | snake  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming, weightlifting
House: modern, cottage, gothic-revival
1. the modern house is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the modern house is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | swimming  |
| House   | gothic-revival    | modern        | cottage |

