.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, alhambra, oliveros
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is between the person driving the quad-bike and the tiparillo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Cigar         | oliveros | alhambra | tiparillo |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian
1. the indonesian is between the person drinking fanta and the brazilian##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Nationality       | canadian  | indonesian | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, mirinda
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking water##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Beverage         | water | mirinda | iced-tea |

