.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, october
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis
1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Birthday   | february       | october | march |
| Sport         | badminton | tennis | rowing      |

