.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, may, april
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, gospel, punk
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in april and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Birthday      | april | may   | march |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco | gospel   |

 